{
    "analysis": "Fault detection identified 33 significant faults across various components and KPIs. Each fault represents consecutive anomalies with threshold breaches exceeding 50% of the extremal value. Since the issue describes a single failure, the next step is to determine the root cause level by identifying the fault with the most significant deviation from the threshold. This will help narrow down the root cause level (e.g., container, service, or node).",
