    "instruction": "Identify the fault with the most significant deviation from the threshold (i.e., the largest percentage breach) among the 33 detected faults. Use this to determine the root cause level (e.g., container, service, or node)."
}

{
    "analysis": "The fault with the most significant deviation from the threshold is associated with the component 'IG01' and KPI 'OSLinux-OSLinux_NETWORK_NETWORK_TCP-FIN-WAIT'. This fault indicates a network-related issue at the node level. Since the issue describes a single failure, the root cause level has been determined to be 'node'. The next step is to confirm whether 'IG01' is the root cause component by analyzing traces to ensure no other node-level components are involved in the failure propagation.",
