    "analysis": "The trace analysis revealed that 'IG01' is not the last faulty node-level component in the failure propagation path. There are 22,174 entries where 'IG01' appears as a parent component, indicating that other node-level components are involved downstream. This suggests that the root cause component may not be 'IG01'. The next step is to analyze logs to identify any critical information or errors related to node-level components, particularly focusing on 'IG01' and its downstream components.",
