    "analysis": "No log data related to node-level components, including 'IG01' and its downstream components, was found in 'log_service.csv' for the specified time range. This suggests that logs do not provide additional insights into the failure propagation or root cause localization. Since traces indicate that 'IG01' is not the last faulty node-level component, and logs do not confirm any critical issues, the root cause component must be determined based on the predominant node-level faults identified in metrics analysis.",
