    "instruction": "The root cause of the failure during the specified time range is determined to be the node-level component 'IG01'. The reason for the failure is a network-related issue, specifically the KPI 'OSLinux-OSLinux_NETWORK_NETWORK_TCP-FIN-WAIT', which exhibited an infinite percentage breach of the threshold. This fault represents the most significant deviation among all detected faults, and no downstream node-level components were identified as the root cause in traces or logs."
